-- Lagardere’s Hachette Livre Is Open to Acquisitions: Les Echos
-- B y   M a r i e   M a w a d
-- 2012-10-08T06:31:20Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-10-08/lagardere-s-hachette-livre-is-open-to-acquisitions-les-echos.html
Hachette Livre, Lagardere’s book
publishing unit, is open to making acquisitions in countries
where its market share isn’t large, Hachette CEO Arnaud Nourry
is cited as saying in an interview with  Les Echos .
*Worldwide consolidation of the book industry will continue,
especially in countries with no price regulation, Nourry says  To contact the reporter on this story:
